00:01:37,034 --> 00:01:38,394
Since time began,

4
00:01:38,673 --> 00:01:40,114
the emperor Pangu

5
00:01:40,834 --> 00:01:42,233
has reigned over the world

6
00:01:42,754 --> 00:01:44,114
and managed the people.

7
00:01:44,353 --> 00:01:45,353
Within Dahuang,

8
00:01:45,754 --> 00:01:47,034
people were conquered.

9
00:01:47,673 --> 00:01:49,434
Since Pangu's death,

10
00:01:49,873 --> 00:01:51,553
wars have raged on

11
00:01:52,114 --> 00:01:53,394
and people have suffered.

12
00:01:53,834 --> 00:01:56,233
Xiyan devotes its strength

13
00:01:56,434 --> 00:01:57,714
to recapturing the Central Plains.

14
00:01:58,273 --> 00:01:59,474
A wise emperor and good officials.

15
00:01:59,913 --> 00:02:01,114
The people are living in peace.

16
00:02:01,474 --> 00:02:04,273
Now, Xiyan will dispatch troops south

17
00:02:04,794 --> 00:02:07,553
into Haoling by the order of Heaven

18
00:02:07,834 --> 00:02:09,073
to maintain order.

19
00:02:10,313 --> 00:02:11,554
To stop people

20
00:02:12,114 --> 00:02:13,313
from misunderstanding us,

21
00:02:13,793 --> 00:02:14,914
we hereby inform them of this.

22
00:02:16,194 --> 00:02:16,914
When troops arrive,

23
00:02:17,713 --> 00:02:18,873
they don't have to escape.

24
00:02:19,354 --> 00:02:21,513
Our orders are strict,

25
00:02:21,834 --> 00:02:23,153
so they won't attack civilians.

26
00:02:23,394 --> 00:02:24,593
Those who surrender

27
00:02:24,953 --> 00:02:27,754
will be treated as the people of Xiyan.

28
00:02:28,274 --> 00:02:29,513
Therefore,

29
00:02:29,953 --> 00:02:31,554
we hereby inform them of this.

30
00:02:36,873 --> 00:02:38,073
(In the first half)

31
00:02:38,233 --> 00:02:39,313
(of March,)

32
00:02:39,914 --> 00:02:41,914
(under the command of Chishui Fenglong,)

33
00:02:42,034 --> 00:02:44,394
(Chishui Xian led a night raid
on Haoling.)

34
00:02:45,073 --> 00:02:46,953
(They quickly occupied Jingdu,)

35
00:02:47,274 --> 00:02:49,394
(south of the Chishui.)

36
00:02:49,994 --> 00:02:50,634
(The next day,)

37
00:02:51,194 --> 00:02:53,754
(the King of Xiyan appointed
Chishui Fenglong as the general)

38
00:02:54,153 --> 00:02:56,114
