to attack Haoling.)

39
00:02:56,873 --> 00:02:59,073
(The Xiyan's army advanced quickly)

40
00:02:59,313 --> 00:03:02,394
(and took two of Haoling's fortresses
within three days.)

41
00:03:02,914 --> 00:03:04,274
(Faced with this sudden change,)

42
00:03:04,713 --> 00:03:07,873
(the entire Dahuang was shocked.)

43
00:03:10,914 --> 00:03:12,354
I heard

44
00:03:12,554 --> 00:03:14,274
General Yu Jiang
has captured two cities of Haoling.

45
00:03:15,313 --> 00:03:16,513
Haoling hasn't been at wars

46
00:03:16,513 --> 00:03:17,873
with others for over ten thousand years.

47
00:03:18,394 --> 00:03:20,513
It has no fighting force

48
00:03:20,834 --> 00:03:21,754
anymore.

49
00:03:22,354 --> 00:03:23,554
But Xiyan is different.

50
00:03:23,953 --> 00:03:26,834
Since its founding,
it has always been at war.

51
00:03:27,474 --> 00:03:29,114
How could Haoling possibly fight it?

52
00:03:29,354 --> 00:03:29,904
Exactly.

53
00:03:30,513 --> 00:03:31,233
If it goes on,

54
00:03:31,554 --> 00:03:32,793
General Chishui will lead the troops

55
00:03:33,153 --> 00:03:35,634
to attack Haoling's capital soon.

56
00:03:38,073 --> 00:03:38,994
Remember

57
00:03:38,994 --> 00:03:40,593
- to check it out before filling it out.
- Okay.

58
00:03:40,593 --> 00:03:41,313
Especially here.

59
00:03:42,114 --> 00:03:43,834
It messes up every time.

60
00:04:10,073 --> 00:04:10,713
Grandfather.

61
00:04:12,433 --> 00:04:13,073
Xiaoyao.

62
00:04:14,394 --> 00:04:14,994
Jing.

63
00:04:15,233 --> 00:04:16,794
Why did those physicians

64
00:04:16,794 --> 00:04:17,674
act a bit strange?

65
00:04:18,074 --> 00:04:18,833
Didn't Cang Xuan

66
00:04:18,833 --> 00:04:20,074
pay their wages?

67
00:04:20,474 --> 00:04:22,113
They didn't work very hard.

68
00:04:24,553 --> 00:04:25,194
What's wrong?

69
00:04:27,393 --> 00:04:27,954
Xiaoyao.

70
00:04:28,514 --> 00:04:29,273
They...

71
00:04:39,313 --> 00:04:39,873
Grandfather.

72
00:04:40,474 --> 00:04:42,153
Are you hiding something from me?

73
00:04:42,553 --> 00:04:43,474
What's going on?

74
00:04:44,113 --> 00:04:45,354
You've grown up.

75
00:04:46,113 --> 00:04:47,234
Ask Cang Xuan

76
00:04:47,833 --> 00:04:49,194
about what happened.

77
00:04:50,113 --> 00:04:51,034
Jing and I

78
00:04:51,393 --> 00:04:54,954
don't want to be blamed for being nosy.

79
00:04:58,833 --> 00:04:59,433
Jing,

80
00:04:59,794 --> 00:05:01,754
play Go with Grandfather.

81
00:05:02,313 --> 00:05:03,634
I'll cook some delicious food

82
00:05:03,674 --> 00:05:04,433
for you.

83
00:05:05,313 --> 00:05:05,914
Okay.

84
00:05:06,474 --> 00:05:07,194
Miao Pu.

85
00:05:07,474 --> 00:05:08,914
Invite His Majesty for dinner.

86
00:05:10,553 --> 00:05:11,194
Yes.

87
00:05:21,474 --> 00:05:22,194
Sit.

88
00:05:24,848 --> 00:05:27,856
(Cheng'en Palace)

89
00:05:28,634 --> 00:05:29,794
Your Majesty, an emergency.

90
00:05:30,074 --> 00:05:31,634
This morning,
Xiyan's army struck Yao City.

91
00:05:31,954 --> 00:05:33,634
Yao City's general Chang Jun
led troops to fight the enemy.

92
00:05:33,873 --> 00:05:34,914
Ultimately, he was defeated

93
00:05:35,234 --> 00:05:35,754
and lost the city.

94
00:05:36,433 --> 00:05:37,713
The war has just begun.

95
00:05:37,873 --> 00:05:39,234
But we have lost three cities.

96
00:05:39,553 --> 00:05:40,144
Well,

97
00:05:40,514 --> 00:05:41,754
what should we do?

98
00:05:43,313 --> 00:05:45,153
These defenders are useless.

99
00:05:45,514 --> 00:05:46,954
Are we going to watch

100
00:05:47,194 --> 00:05:49,113
Xiyan's army capture our capital?

101
00:05:49,474 --> 00:05:50,113
Cang Xuan

102
00:05:50,194 --> 00:05:51,234
started the war suddenly.

103
00:05:51,514 --> 00:05:52,393
He's so ungrateful

104
00:05:52,474 --> 00:05:53,273
and shameless

105
00:05:53,433 --> 00:05:54,393
with ruthless ambition.

106
00:05:54,713 --> 00:05:55,433
If we had known this,

107
00:05:55,674 --> 00:05:56,634
we should not have let him

108
00:05:56,634 --> 00:05:57,914
leave Haoling alive.

109
00:05:57,914 --> 00:05:58,512
That's right.

110
00:05:58,634 --> 00:06:00,433
After talking so much,

111
00:06:00,914 --> 00:06:03,354
do you have any strategy
to counter the enemy?

112
00:06:05,113 --> 00:06:06,354
If you don't have any strategy,

113
00:06:06,993 --> 00:06:08,954
is anyone willing to fight the enemy?

114
00:06:10,593 --> 00:06:11,184
Your Majesty.

115
00:06:11,914 --> 00:06:13,313
I'm willing to lead troops into battle.

116
00:06:15,634 --> 00:06:16,833
So am I.

117
00:06:21,354 --> 00:06:21,873
Your Majesty.

118
00:06:22,514 --> 00:06:24,514
I've learned a lot
from Your Majesty these years.

119
00:06:24,634 --> 00:06:26,234
Finally, I can put my learning into use.

120
00:06:26,794 --> 00:06:29,113
I request Your Majesty's permission
to go into battle.

121
00:06:29,194 --> 00:06:30,993
Please, Your Majesty.

122
00:06:34,113 --> 00:06:34,634
Ru Shou.

123
00:06:35,514 --> 00:06:36,754
I appoint you as the commander,

124
00:06:37,153 --> 00:06:38,273
Qin Mang as the vanguard.

125
00:06:38,474 --> 00:06:39,313
You lead the troops.

126
00:06:39,954 --> 00:06:40,514
Qinglong,

127
00:06:40,873 --> 00:06:41,433
Baihu,

128
00:06:41,954 --> 00:06:42,754
Changxi,

129
00:06:42,954 --> 00:06:45,713
and Xihe shall all follow orders.

130
00:06:45,754 --> 00:06:47,113
- I will, Your Majesty.
- I will, Your Majesty.

131
00:07:18,313 --> 00:07:19,433
This time, I learned

132
00:07:19,433 --> 00:07:20,833
to make this from someone.

133
00:07:21,433 --> 00:07:22,313
If you don't like it,

134
00:07:22,474 --> 00:07:23,914
just take it as a fangle.

135
00:07:24,674 --> 00:07:25,553
You made it.

136
00:07:25,553 --> 00:07:26,514
Of course, I like it.

137
00:07:42,914 --> 00:07:44,313
It's a pity it's not winter.

138
00:07:44,634 --> 00:07:45,553
I can't see plum blossoms.

139
00:08:40,554 --> 00:08:41,273
Your Highness.

140
00:09:16,513 --> 00:09:18,513
This is between Cang Xuan and me.

141
00:09:19,554 --> 00:09:20,914
It has nothing to do with you.

142
00:09:22,273 --> 00:09:24,314
Cang Xuan is still your brother.

143
00:09:39,633 --> 00:09:40,234
Father.

144
00:09:41,474 --> 00:09:42,753
Since he started a war with you,

145
00:09:42,914 --> 00:09:44,474
he's no longer my brother.

146
00:09:45,434 --> 00:09:46,753
You took him as an apprentice

147
00:09:46,953 --> 00:09:48,354
and taught him with great care.

148
00:09:49,034 --> 00:09:50,674
How could he be so cruel?

149
00:09:51,393 --> 00:09:53,393
Cang Xuan is my apprentice.

150
00:09:54,073 --> 00:09:55,674
He's also Xiyan's ruler.

151
00:09:56,914 --> 00:09:58,393
If he forgets his duty as emperor

152
00:09:59,273 --> 00:10:01,554
because of personal affection,

153
00:10:03,034 --> 00:10:04,753
I will be disappointed in him.

154
00:10:05,794 --> 00:10:06,794
And what about my sister?

155
00:10:07,234 --> 00:10:08,833
Why didn't she try to stop him?

156
00:10:09,474 --> 00:10:11,554
Though she is
not your biological daughter,

157
00:10:11,914 --> 00:10:12,794
she has been

158
00:10:12,794 --> 00:10:14,314
the Princess of Haoling
for so many years.

159
00:10:14,994 --> 00:10:15,753
Could she

160
00:10:17,874 --> 00:10:20,114
watch the downfall of Haoling?

161
00:10:46,633 --> 00:10:47,153
Brother.

162
00:10:47,354 --> 00:10:48,153
You said before

163
00:10:48,153 --> 00:10:49,393
that you liked this dish.

164
00:10:49,914 --> 00:10:50,753
I made it.

165
00:10:50,953 --> 00:10:51,713
You try it.

166
00:10:51,794 --> 00:10:52,336
Alright.

167
00:10:56,393 --> 00:10:57,593
Today, I found that Grandfather

168
00:10:57,633 --> 00:10:58,474
and those physicians

169
00:10:58,474 --> 00:10:59,593
were very strange.

170
00:11:00,874 --> 00:11:01,434
Brother.

171
00:11:01,874 --> 00:11:02,633
Can you tell me

172
00:11:02,633 --> 00:11:03,674
what has happened?

173
00:11:18,474 --> 00:11:19,914
As long as I go down the mountain,

174
00:11:20,153 --> 00:11:21,354
I will figure it out.

175
00:11:22,753 --> 00:11:23,674
But I hope

176
00:11:24,593 --> 00:11:25,833
that you will tell me about it.

177
00:11:40,713 --> 00:11:41,914
I sent troops

178
00:11:42,513 --> 00:11:43,593
to attack Haoling.

179
00:11:46,713 --> 00:11:47,474
Cang Xuan.

180
00:11:49,193 --> 00:11:50,273
What did you say?

181
00:11:56,114 --> 00:11:56,794
I...

182
00:11:59,354 --> 00:12:00,234
I sent troops

183
00:12:00,953 --> 00:12:01,753
to attack Haoling.

184
00:12:09,994 --> 00:12:10,593
Xiaoyao.

185
00:12:11,314 --> 00:12:11,994
Xiaoyao.

186
00:12:13,794 --> 00:12:15,153
Play Go with me.

187
00:12:29,114 --> 00:12:29,713
Xiaoyao.

188
00:12:30,593 --> 00:12:32,474
Xiaoyao, open the door. Let me explain.

189
00:12:32,753 --> 00:12:33,633
What are you going to say?

190
00:12:33,953 --> 00:12:35,153
Do you remember?

191
00:12:35,393 --> 00:12:36,393
When you were driven desperate

192
00:12:36,434 --> 00:12:37,314
by your uncles back then,

193
00:12:37,314 --> 00:12:38,674
the King of Haoling took you in.

194
00:12:39,314 --> 00:12:41,434
He took you as an apprentice,

195
00:12:41,833 --> 00:12:43,593
teaching you
to play the zither, brew wine,

196
00:12:43,593 --> 00:12:44,914
improve the people's livelihood,

197
00:12:45,073 --> 00:12:46,193
deal with state affairs,

198
00:12:46,273 --> 00:12:47,593
and train secret guards for you.

199
00:12:48,153 --> 00:12:49,474
Xiaoyao, you don't understand.

200
00:12:49,874 --> 00:12:50,753
I don't understand?

201
00:12:51,474 --> 00:12:52,833
Then explain it to me clearly.

202
00:12:53,513 --> 00:12:54,554
What I just said

203
00:12:54,554 --> 00:12:55,513
is false?

204
00:12:55,713 --> 00:12:56,794
Xiaoyao,

205
00:12:56,794 --> 00:12:58,073
you were telling the truth.

206
00:12:59,073 --> 00:13:00,434
But there are many other things

207
00:13:00,434 --> 00:13:01,393
that you don't know about.

208
00:13:01,393 --> 00:13:02,713
If it weren't for him,

209
00:13:02,713 --> 00:13:04,273
we wouldn't have become orphans.

210
00:13:04,513 --> 00:13:05,953
I wouldn't have needed his shelter.

211
00:13:05,953 --> 00:13:07,434
And you wouldn't have had to be homeless

212
00:13:07,434 --> 00:13:09,674
for over 300 years.

213
00:13:11,794 --> 00:13:12,434
What did you say?

214
00:13:13,073 --> 00:13:13,994
I don't understand.

215
00:13:16,273 --> 00:13:17,314
Back then, Auntie found out

216
00:13:17,314 --> 00:13:18,874
about Chenrong Yanzhuan's conspiracy

217
00:13:18,874 --> 00:13:22,393
and begged the King of Haoling
to save my father.

218
00:13:30,354 --> 00:13:31,073
Your Majesty.

219
00:13:31,513 --> 00:13:33,073
(Xiling Heng)
Please lend me an army

220
00:13:33,874 --> 00:13:34,874
to save Zhongyi.

221
00:13:35,073 --> 00:13:36,114
Please rise first.

222
00:13:46,354 --> 00:13:47,073
Your Majesty.

223
00:13:51,034 --> 00:13:53,034
It's not a small thing.

224
00:13:53,753 --> 00:13:56,633
Troops are so precious to every nation.

225
00:13:57,513 --> 00:13:59,153
Can you guarantee the safety

226
00:13:59,234 --> 00:14:00,953
of Haoling's soldiers?

227
00:14:14,994 --> 00:14:15,674
Heng.

228
00:14:22,833 --> 00:14:24,794
By cutting a finger,

229
00:14:27,753 --> 00:14:29,994
I swear I'll ensure the safety
of Haoling's soldiers.

230
00:14:30,914 --> 00:14:31,953
Your Majesty,

231
00:14:33,314 --> 00:14:34,953
please lend me an army.

232
00:14:39,874 --> 00:14:41,593
Auntie cut one of her fingers

233
00:14:42,953 --> 00:14:46,193
and implored the King of Haoling
to save my father.

234
00:14:48,513 --> 00:14:49,753
But he refused.

235
00:14:53,593 --> 00:14:55,874
Xiaoyao, he refused.

236
00:15:00,753 --> 00:15:02,273
No wonder when I asked my mother

237
00:15:02,273 --> 00:15:04,674
about her broken finger,
she didn't tell me.

238
00:15:08,034 --> 00:15:09,593
No wonder my mother

239
00:15:09,593 --> 00:15:11,513
divorced my father

240
00:15:12,193 --> 00:15:13,794
after your father died.

241
00:15:15,513 --> 00:15:16,193
Moreover,

242
00:15:17,593 --> 00:15:18,994
Haoling also took part in the battle

243
00:15:20,153 --> 00:15:21,513
between Xiyan and Chenrong.

244
00:15:21,994 --> 00:15:22,994
Your father and mother

245
00:15:22,994 --> 00:15:24,994
met each other on the battlefield.

246
00:15:24,994 --> 00:15:27,234
The King of Haoling is also to blame.

247
00:15:48,914 --> 00:15:49,554
Xiaoyao.

248
00:15:52,273 --> 00:15:53,073
Xiaoyao.

249
00:15:53,794 --> 00:15:54,794
Perhaps it cannot

250
00:15:54,794 --> 00:15:56,554
be entirely blamed on Master.

251
00:15:59,034 --> 00:16:00,434
But whenever I think

252
00:16:00,434 --> 00:16:02,073
that my father could have lived,

253
00:16:03,593 --> 00:16:05,753
my mother didn't have to kill herself
before my eyes,

254
00:16:05,753 --> 00:16:07,554
Grandma could have lived longer,

255
00:16:07,554 --> 00:16:09,354
Auntie didn't have to go to war,

256
00:16:10,713 --> 00:16:12,034
and you didn't have to leave me,

257
00:16:14,593 --> 00:16:15,554
I really

258
00:16:18,593 --> 00:16:19,953
can't only

259
00:16:19,953 --> 00:16:22,474
regard him as my master.

260
00:16:52,633 --> 00:16:53,314
Great Emperor.

261
00:16:54,073 --> 00:16:54,672
I...

262
00:16:54,753 --> 00:16:56,554
This is between him and his sister.

263
00:16:57,114 --> 00:16:58,633
Let them resolve it themselves.

264
00:16:59,434 --> 00:17:00,713
Cang Xuan is an emperor.

265
00:17:01,073 --> 00:17:03,953
He could allow Xiaoyao
to throw a cup at him.

266
00:17:04,153 --> 00:17:06,834
And he's even begging
for her forgiveness.

267
00:17:07,834 --> 00:17:10,794
But he may not permit an outsider

268
00:17:11,194 --> 00:17:13,314
to see his embarrassment.

269
00:17:19,353 --> 00:17:23,473
Cang Xuan and Xiaoyao
have faced hardships since childhood.

270
00:17:24,473 --> 00:17:26,753
They almost lost all their relatives.

271
00:17:27,314 --> 00:17:28,233
Over these years,

272
00:17:28,633 --> 00:17:30,353
the two of them have been inseparable

273
00:17:30,873 --> 00:17:32,314
and relying on each other.

274
00:17:32,794 --> 00:17:33,714
Sometimes,

275
00:17:34,314 --> 00:17:35,594
I am also an outsider

276
00:17:36,153 --> 00:17:37,794
to them.

277
00:17:46,393 --> 00:17:47,353
I see.

278
00:17:47,914 --> 00:17:49,113
Thank you for your reminding.

279
00:17:49,633 --> 00:17:51,473
You are a clever child.

280
00:17:53,034 --> 00:17:53,674
Sit.

281
00:18:21,153 --> 00:18:21,914
Xiaoyao.

282
00:18:23,674 --> 00:18:25,074
Xiaoyao, can you open the door?

283
00:18:25,954 --> 00:18:27,513
We can talk face to face.

284
00:18:29,873 --> 00:18:31,233
No wonder you hate him.

285
00:18:34,074 --> 00:18:35,714
I even want to hate him too.

286
00:18:36,473 --> 00:18:37,714
