00:35:36,753 --> 00:35:38,034
(from Xiaoyao's body soon.)

570
00:36:54,953 --> 00:36:56,433
Why haven't you rested yet,
foster father?

571
00:36:57,433 --> 00:36:59,074
You are not resting, either.

572
00:37:03,554 --> 00:37:04,874
I just came out and had a look.

573
00:37:07,713 --> 00:37:09,634
How long can the lights

574
00:37:10,193 --> 00:37:12,154
in the camp last?

575
00:37:13,834 --> 00:37:15,673
Haoling is at war with Haoling.

576
00:37:15,913 --> 00:37:16,993
If Xiyan wins,

577
00:37:18,114 --> 00:37:19,673
its next target

578
00:37:19,834 --> 00:37:20,794
will be us.

579
00:37:22,193 --> 00:37:23,193
You know

580
00:37:23,594 --> 00:37:25,993
we stand no chance
against the Xiyan's army.

581
00:37:29,794 --> 00:37:30,554
Yes, I do.

582
00:37:31,874 --> 00:37:33,554
We serve Chenrong.

583
00:37:34,594 --> 00:37:36,074
Our soldiers will fight

584
00:37:36,074 --> 00:37:37,753
to the last man.

585
00:37:39,193 --> 00:37:40,713
You don't have to stay

586
00:37:41,314 --> 00:37:43,114
to join us in this deadly war.

587
00:37:44,753 --> 00:37:46,354
You have done enough
for the Chenrong Army

588
00:37:46,513 --> 00:37:47,554
to repay the favor

589
00:37:47,594 --> 00:37:49,513
you owed me.

590
00:37:49,913 --> 00:37:50,834
- You...
- Foster father.

591
00:38:00,874 --> 00:38:01,713
Never mind.

592
00:38:02,753 --> 00:38:04,233
Anyway, it's just death.

593
00:38:05,394 --> 00:38:06,554
It's no big deal.

594
00:38:24,594 --> 00:38:25,168
Grandfather.

595
00:38:27,874 --> 00:38:29,154
Xiaoyao is not at home again?

596
00:38:29,953 --> 00:38:31,154
Recently,

597
00:38:31,554 --> 00:38:34,193
she has been leaving early
and returning late.

598
00:38:34,673 --> 00:38:38,314
She is not here today.

599
00:38:39,834 --> 00:38:40,953
I'm afraid she will be away

600
00:38:41,193 --> 00:38:42,794
tomorrow and the day after.

601
00:38:43,713 --> 00:38:45,473
I know she's avoiding me.

602
00:38:46,354 --> 00:38:47,753
Even so,

603
00:38:48,314 --> 00:38:49,554
you still come here every day?

604
00:38:53,673 --> 00:38:54,394
Let me help.

605
00:38:57,354 --> 00:38:58,713
Xiaoyao isn't here,

606
00:39:00,233 --> 00:39:01,673
but I can keep you company.

607
00:39:01,834 --> 00:39:03,993
I can play Go and drink tea with you.

608
00:39:05,673 --> 00:39:07,273
I'm glad to hear that.

609
00:39:08,554 --> 00:39:11,874
Given what you've experienced
as an emperor,

610
00:39:12,433 --> 00:39:13,913
I feel bad for you.

611
00:39:14,114 --> 00:39:15,354
I've done what I should do

612
00:39:15,394 --> 00:39:16,913
as a ruler of a country.

613
00:39:17,354 --> 00:39:17,953
I want

614
00:39:18,913 --> 00:39:20,554
to be myself at home.

615
00:39:30,704 --> 00:39:36,912
(Rejuvenation Hall)

616
00:39:46,513 --> 00:39:47,074
Miss.

617
00:39:47,273 --> 00:39:48,354
Are we going back?

618
00:39:48,834 --> 00:39:49,513
No, I'm not.

619
00:39:50,233 --> 00:39:51,034
Where are we going?

620
00:39:54,794 --> 00:39:55,794
Just strolling around.

621
00:39:55,811 --> 00:40:02,288
(Rejuvenation Hall)

622
00:40:10,034 --> 00:40:10,640
Xiang Liu.

623
00:40:11,473 --> 00:40:12,513
You have mighty spirit power

624
00:40:12,673 --> 00:40:13,473
and nine lives.

625
00:40:13,594 --> 00:40:14,794
But Xiaoyao does not.

626
00:40:17,354 --> 00:40:18,953
I just want to confirm one thing.

627
00:40:19,993 --> 00:40:21,473
If you are in danger,

628
00:40:22,513 --> 00:40:23,953
will Xiaoyao be implicated?

629
00:40:25,193 --> 00:40:26,314
You will know

630
00:40:27,154 --> 00:40:28,034
when I die.

631
00:40:28,473 --> 00:40:29,753
I must know it right now.

632
00:40:30,874 --> 00:40:31,473
Please help me

633
00:40:31,473 --> 00:40:32,953
remove the poisonous bug from Xiaoyao.

634
00:40:33,634 --> 00:40:34,594
I can give you high rewards.

635
00:40:34,673 --> 00:40:35,554
I can't help.

636
00:40:37,394 --> 00:40:38,594
Cang Xuan removed it successfully.

637
00:40:38,993 --> 00:40:39,794
Why can't Xiaoyao?

638
00:40:40,074 --> 00:40:41,473
I'm not Cang Xuan.

639
00:40:42,114 --> 00:40:43,034
I am Xiang Liu.

640
00:40:43,513 --> 00:40:46,554
I can't remove the poisonous bug.

641
00:40:47,034 --> 00:40:48,834
If you help Xiaoyao
remove the poisonous bug,

642
00:40:49,554 --> 00:40:51,594
I can give you as much grain
and forage as you want.

643
00:40:51,874 --> 00:40:53,794
You have provided 37 years

644
00:40:53,794 --> 00:40:55,233
of army provisions.

645
00:40:55,713 --> 00:40:56,874
You can provide more,

646
00:40:57,473 --> 00:40:58,834
but the Chenrong Army

647
00:41:00,634 --> 00:41:02,634
won't have another 37 years.

648
00:41:13,074 --> 00:41:13,834
There is no other way

649
00:41:13,834 --> 00:41:14,753
to remove the bug?

650
00:41:15,314 --> 00:41:15,993
No.

651
00:41:56,273 --> 00:41:56,913
Xiang Liu.

652
00:42:01,513 --> 00:42:02,713
Miss, you've been following me.

653
00:42:02,993 --> 00:42:03,993
Why?

654
00:42:12,114 --> 00:42:13,673
Since you've been doing this,

655
00:42:14,154 --> 00:42:14,993
could you

656
00:42:16,634 --> 00:42:17,713
have feelings for me?

657
00:42:19,114 --> 00:42:19,713
Xiang Liu.

658
00:42:20,354 --> 00:42:21,273
Stop pretending.

659
00:42:21,834 --> 00:42:22,753
I know it's you.

660
00:42:27,753 --> 00:42:30,034
Don't you feel shy?

661
00:42:30,233 --> 00:42:31,034
If you don't let go,

662
00:42:31,834 --> 00:42:33,233
don't blame me for being rude.

663
00:42:33,594 --> 00:42:34,193
Fine.

664
00:42:34,713 --> 00:42:35,753
Go ahead.

665
00:42:36,713 --> 00:42:38,114
Anyway, if I'm in pain,

666
00:42:38,433 --> 00:42:39,554
you will feel the same.

667
00:42:58,394 --> 00:42:59,713
You have so many faces.

668
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

669
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

670
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

671
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

672
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

673
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

674
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

675
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

676
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

677
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

678
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

679
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

680
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

681
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

682
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

683
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
